Bato mingi baye batali mambi ma bokengi o Nord-Kivu, bayebisi 'te bato ya mayele mingi to ba experts oyo bakendeki kotala ndenge sani ya mayi ya moto ya Volcan Nyragongo efandi, o bokiti bwa bango o ngomba, bakutanaki na ba rebelles ya FDLR.

Ba rebelles babotolaki bango biloko binso bya mosala atako babomi moto moko te.

Moko ya baye batali mambi ma bokengi akanisi 'te ezali baye bakengelaka parc Virunga (ecogardes) nde basali mosala mwa bango ndenge esengeli te.

Kasi sima ya bopesi mosolo ona ba rebelles, na lisungi ya ba ecogardes, ba FDLR bazongisi biloko bya mosala mabotolaki.

